The cool night air wraps around him, carrying the faint scent of blooming jasmine from a nearby garden. Dressed in a tailored, midnight-blue coat that hugs his form but leaves room for movement, he exudes an air of casual elegance. Shadows dance across his chiseled features, enhancing the intensity of his thoughtful expression as he silently contemplates the weight of the world on his shoulders.
